    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We intend to use AI for almost all aspects of drug discovery but currently we are using the structural properties of artificial intelligence to discover novel<br></br>drug targets capable of using generative Machine Learning models. We are always keeping an eye out for knowledgeable and interested volunteers who wish to contribute to the research. Varsha is coordinating this work and can be reached at <strong>AIDrugDiscoveryVolunteer@ioncurerx.com</strong> if you wish to volunteer with our group.</p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>